title: RoboFish: A Mindy and Guy Raz Production
description:
Lights... Camera... Action!! Mindy is making a movie based on new research from the University of Western Australia starring Guy Raz as... Robofish, a robotic fish that fights off invasive predators! It's the who, what, when, where, how and WOW of robotic fish!
